# TypeScript Configuration for Deployment Scripts

This tsconfig is specifically for deployment scripts that use Hardhat.

{
  "extends": "./backend/tsconfig.json",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "rootDir": ".",
    "outDir": "./dist",
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "skipLibCheck": true
  },
  "include": [
    "hardhat.config.ts",
    "backend/scripts/**/*.ts",
    "scripts/**/*.ts"
  ],
  "exclude": [
    "node_modules",
    "backend/src",
    "backend/dist"
  ]
}
